column2: SELECT FLOOR (petroMag_r-#*log1# (dbo.fCosmoDl (s.z) )#-extinction_r) as M, COUNT (*) as count FROM SpecObj s INNER JOIN PhotoObj ON s.bestObjID = PhotoObj.ObjID WHERE s.z BETWEEN # AND # AND objTypeName = # GROUP BY FLOOR (petroMag_r-#*log1# (dbo.fCosmoDl (s.z) )#-extinction_r) ORDER BY #
